**********Табицы******

GET admin/posts PostsController@index
GET admin/posts/create PostsController@create
POST admin/posts PostsController@store
GET admin/posts/{id}/edit PostsController@edit
PUT admin/posts/{id} PostsController@update
DELETE admin/posts/{id}/delete PostsController@destroy


=========================================

создание ядра проекта Model (бизнес-логика)

php artisan make:model Category -m
php artisan make:model Tag -m
php artisan make:model Comment -m
php artisan make:model Post -m
php artisan make:model Subscription -m

php artisan make:migration create_posts_tags_table --create=post_tags

php artisan migrate

php artisan migrate:refresh
















